race.comment: GIRLDONTGOAWAYMAD (5) made an encouraging debut last time out, finishing 6 lengths from the winner in third over 1106m at this track (Dirt). Open to improvement and looks a serious contender. I MIGHT BE TROUBLE (10) wasn't far away on debut last start over 1308m at this track (Dirt), finishing fourth and beaten 5 lengths. Can open winning account this time. SHAKE THAT THING (9) stepped out for the first time last start and was just fair in finishing fifth at this track (Dirt) over 1308m, beaten 5 lengths. One of the main contenders. LIL MISS BRISKET (4) was safely held on debut last start, finishing 11 lengths behind the winner in fourth over 1106m at this track (Dirt). Will take a lot from that experience. Can improve.
